trump.name: Official Trump
trump.news: The $TRUMP token, a PolitiFi cryptocurrency inspired by President Donald Trump, climbed over 13% in the last 24 hours to around $8.30, marking a 40% weekly gain from $6 lows. The rise aligns with anticipation for Trump's October 30 meeting with Chinese President Xi Jinping in South Korea, where officials finalized a trade framework to pause tariffs and boost U.S. exports like soybeans. Trading volume jumped 755% to $2.26 billion, though some X influencers warn of potential manipulation and overbought conditions.
